# Introduction

This repository is the demo application for the article entitled [Popular Users per Language and Region with Silex and Github](http://www.sitepoint.com/popular-users-per-language-region-silex-github/), published on SitePoint. To run this application, do the following:

1. Set your document root to the `web` directory of wherever you clone this package to.
2. Run `composer install` to install the dependencies.
3. Open `http://<your-configured-hostname>/creators/<location>/<language>` to see the app in action.

If you get any issues or have any feedback, feel free to open an issue or send in a pull request.